entry.summary:
We have presented four papers [1, 2, 3, 4] at the 12th International Congress on Engineered Material Platforms for Novel Wave Phenomena (Metamaterials), Espoo, Finland, Aug. 27-30, 2018.
Scaravilli, M., Micco, A., Castaldi, G., Coppola, G., Gioffrè, Iodice, M., … Cusano, A. (2018). Fiber-tip coupling of Bloch surface waves. In International Congress on Engineered Material Platforms for Novel Wave Phenomena (METAMATERIALS). Espoo, Finland, Aug. 27-30, 2018.
